{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779252900692,"sessionID":"ses_1bc4b4b8cffe0nK0wwHHNx2kzK","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_00_CKV09nnyS11MSZgifyD17527","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/status/INTEGRATION_REPORT.md"},"output":"<path>/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/status/INTEGRATION_REPORT.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Integration Report — nestfind\n2: \n3: phase: integrate\n4: endpoints_wired: 34\n5: services_created: 8\n6: hooks_created: 7\n7: pages_updated: 17\n8: pages_total: 22\n9: pages_with_hooks: 17\n10: coverage_pct: 77\n11: rule_i1_interceptor_retry_flag: true\n12: rule_i3_route_matching: true\n13: \n14: ---\n15: \n16: ## Summary\n17: \n18: All frontend pages wired to backend API endpoints using TanStack Query (useQuery for reads, useMutation for writes). Every API call includes loading, error, and empty states. The Axios instance uses httpOnly cookies with `_isRetry` flag to prevent infinite refresh loops (RULE-I1). No `setTimeout(() => navigate(...))` patterns (RULE-I2). All types use explicit DTOs — no `any` types in response handlers.\n19: \n20: ---\n21: \n22: ## Infrastructure Changes\n23: \n24: ### Axios Instance (`services/httpService.ts`)\n25: - Switched from `localStorage` token to httpOnly cookies (`withCredentials: true`)\n26: - Added `_isRetry` flag on `InternalAxiosRequestConfig` via module augmentation\n27: - 401 handler: attempts `/auth/refresh`, retries original request; on failure redirects to `/login`\n28: - Timeout increased to 30s for file uploads\n29: - Added `patch()` method\n30: \n31: ### QueryClientProvider (`hooks/providers/providers.tsx`)\n32: - Wrapped app in `QueryClientProvider` with `QueryClient`\n33: - Default options: 1min staleTime, 1 retry, no refetchOnWindowFocus\n34: \n35: ---\n36: \n37: ## Services Created\n38: \n39: | Service | File | Endpoints Covered |\n40: |---------|------|-------------------|\n41: | authService | `services/api/authService.ts` | /auth/login, /auth/register, /auth/logout, /auth/refresh, /auth/me, /auth/forgot-password, /auth/reset-password |\n42: | propertyService | `services/api/propertyService.ts` | GET/POST /properties, GET/PATCH/DELETE /properties/:id, POST /properties/:id/photos, DELETE /properties/:id/photos/:photoId, PATCH photos/primary, PATCH photos/reorder |\n43: | favoriteService | `services/api/favoriteService.ts` | GET/POST /favorites, DELETE /favorites/:propertyId |\n44: | inquiryService | `services/api/inquiryService.ts` | POST /properties/:id/inquiries, GET /inquiries, GET/PATCH /inquiries/:id, POST /inquiries/:id/respond |\n45: | adminService | `services/api/adminService.ts` | GET /admin/dashboard, GET /admin/users, GET /admin/users/:id, PATCH /admin/users/:id/status |\n46: | amenityService | `services/api/amenityService.ts` | GET/POST /amenities, PATCH/DELETE /amenities/:id |\n47: | profileService | `services/api/profileService.ts` | GET/PATCH /profile |\n48: \n49: ---\n50: \n51: ## TanStack Query Hooks Created\n52: \n53: | Hook File | Exports |\n54: |-----------|---------|\n55: | `useAuth.ts` | useLogin, useRegister, useLogout, useCurrentUser, useForgotPassword, useResetPassword |\n56: | `useProperties.ts` | usePropertySearch, usePropertyDetail, useCreateProperty, useUpdateProperty, useDeleteProperty |\n57: | `useFavorites.ts` | useFavoriteList, useAddFavorite, useRemoveFavorite |\n58: | `useInquiries.ts` | useSubmitInquiry, useInquiryList, useInquiryDetail, useMarkInquiryAsRead, useRespondToInquiry |\n59: | `useAdmin.ts` | useDashboardStats, useAdminUserList, useAdminUserDetail, useUpdateUserStatus |\n60: | `useAmenities.ts` | useAmenityList, useCreateAmenity, useUpdateAmenity, useDeleteAmenity |\n61: | `useProfile.ts` | useProfile, useUpdateProfile |\n62: \n63: ---\n64: \n65: ## Pages Wired\n66: \n67: | Page | Hooks Used | States |\n68: |------|-----------|--------|\n69: | `admin/dashboard.tsx` | useDashboardStats | loading, error, success with stat cards + recent lists |\n70: | `admin/properties.tsx` | usePropertySearch, useDeleteProperty | loading, error, empty (no properties), paginated table |\n71: | `admin/property-form.tsx` | useCreateProperty, useUpdateProperty, useAmenityList, usePropertyDetail | loading, error, submission feedback, amenity checkboxes |\n72: | `admin/inquiries.tsx` | useInquiryList, useMarkInquiryAsRead, useRespondToInquiry | loading, error, empty, status filter, paginated table |\n73: | `admin/users.tsx` | useAdminUserList, useUpdateUserStatus | loading, error, empty, paginated table, status toggle |\n74: | `renter/search.tsx` | usePropertySearch, useAddFavorite, useRemoveFavorite | loading, error, empty (no results), filter chips, grid + pagination |\n75: | `renter/detail.tsx` | usePropertyDetail, useAddFavorite, useRemoveFavorite, useSubmitInquiry | loading, error, empty (not found), photos, amenities, inquiry form |\n76: | `renter/favorites.tsx` | useFavoriteList, useRemoveFavorite | loading, error, empty (no favorites), grid display |\n77: | `auth/login.tsx` | useLogin | form validation (zod), pending state, error state |\n78: | `auth/register.tsx` | useRegister | form validation (zod), pending state, error state |\n79: | `auth/signup.tsx` | useRegister | form validation (zod), pending state, error state |\n80: | `auth/forgot-password.tsx` | useForgotPassword | pending, success, error states |\n81: | `auth/reset-password.tsx` | useResetPassword | pending, success, error states, token from URL params |\n82: | `auth/admin-login.tsx` | useLogin | pending, error states |\n83: | `profile.tsx` | useProfile, useUpdateProfile | loading, error, update pending/error/success |\n84: | `landing.tsx` | usePropertySearch | empty (coming soon), grid display of featured properties |\n85: | `renter/inquiries.tsx` | useInquiryList | loading, error, empty (no inquiries), table with property links, status badges, dates |\n86: \